3-Buttons

-add the font awesome icons and materialize button to the top of the file and also the normal css and js links
STANDAR BUTTONS
1-create two standard buttons, one with a button tag and the other with a link tag (<a>)
WAVE EFFECT
2-create one with a button tag and the other with a link tag (<a>) and use the wave affect:
btn waves-effect waves-light.
WAVE COLORS
3-create five buttons.
Give them different waves color using the class:
btn white red-text waves-effect waves-red
ICONS
